CORRECTION: Paley tournaments exist only for p≡3 mod 4!
  p=3: ≡3 mod 4 → QR_3 is a tournament (the 3-cycle)
  p=5: ≡1 mod 4 → NO Paley tournament (QR_5 not a tournament)
  p=7: ≡3 mod 4 → QR_7 is a valid Paley tournament
  p=11: ≡3 mod 4 → QR_11 is a valid Paley tournament

